snippet.title: An Outcry. Release Trailer.
snippet.description:
PLAY HERE:
STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1817470/An_Outcry/
ITCH: https://quinnk.itch.io/an-outcry

FOLLOW HERE:
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/AnOutcryGame

An Outcry is a narrative horror game parable made in RPG Maker 2003. Follow the Unnamed's journey into the harshest night of their life; 
Harass your neighbours. Debate with birds. Smoke to survive.

Trailer editing, Visual effects and live-action performance by Amos Sorri
https://twitter.com/AmosSorri
